body: Trumpy, hi. I don't know if we'll cross paths with you yet before the New Year or not, so briefly: I've moved everyone on the blog until January 7, as discussed with you earlier. the negotiations are under control, you can probably see. Today I won't be long, because I'm getting ready and planning a departure in the evening for 700 km, the road is not close and the fucking snow...the case is short). Tomorrow will still appear in chats to close tails, if any. After N.G. I'll probably come and first thing I'll buy a car))), since the fall in the bitcoin I don't have enough money for a square. Well, Happy New Year to you and your family, all your good wishes, happiness and good luck in the coming year, more children's laughter, less tears, because for the sake of that we fuck with you and here. If anything, write here, I'll show up periodically as I can and respond to your cries))
